channel.title: [Delta]Supremacy | Where everyone matters
channel.description:
[center][b]Introduction:[/b][/center] [tt]Hello moparscape and welcome to the [b]Supremacy[/b] development thread. I am using Delta as my base. Believe me, if I thought I wouldn't get anywhere with this development, I wouldn't be wasting my time. I think with a little hard work and patience, I could make something great out of Delta. Anyways, I started this project back in November of 2011 and I took a break (family problems) but now i'm back, and I am hard at work. I will have updates posted on a daily basis. As of now, I am working on rewriting some of the skills. My main goal is to make Delta as stable as possible. I know this will take alot of work/time, but I am sticking with this project no matter what.[/tt]
[center][b]Future updates/goals:[/b][/center] [tt]I only have 2 main goals as of now, they consist of rewriting every skill and cleaning out every class file to make this project as stable as possible. I know what you're thinking, "Delta being stable? haha!" Well, as I have said, I believe I can achieve this as time progresses.[/tt]
[center][b]Skills:[/b][/center] R[tt]ight now, I have the basic skills, but I am working on rewriting all of them with the correct level requirments, etc. At this point in time, combat is the most important to me. As most of you know, Delta's combat system isn't all that great. My goal is to perfect it. I will post pictures in the near future.[/tt]
[b]Media:[/b] [IMG]http://i41.tinypic.com/239nc1.png[/img] [i]Spells with the correct level/rune requirements. (Will post video soon)[/i] [IMG]http://i39.tinypic.com/vrx6x1.png[/img]
[i]Please, if you have any suggestions, post them below![/i]
[b]Note:[/b] This thread will be updated frequently.
